### TextToSqlAgent - Agentic AI Testing Suite
### Test all new features from Phase 1 & 2 refactor

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@devEndpoint = {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/dev

### ============================================
### Test 1: Health Check
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/health

### Expected: Status 200, Service: "TextToSqlAgent API"

### ============================================
### Test 2: Check Agent Mode
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/mode

### Expected: Mode: "ReAct", Description mentions "autonomous reasoning"

### ============================================
### Test 3: Simple Query (ReAct Agent)
### ============================================
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me all customers"
}

### Expected:
### - success: true
### - metadata.agent_type: "ReAct"
### - metadata.total_steps: 3-5
### - sqlGenerated: SELECT query
### - answer: Contains result count

### ============================================
### Test 4: Complex Multi-Step Query
### ============================================
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the average order value for customers in New York?"
}

### Expected:
### - Multiple steps visible in processingSteps
### - Step 1: explore_schema
### - Step 2: generate_sql (with JOIN and AVG)
### - Step 3: execute_sql
### - Step 4: finish

### ============================================
### Test 5: Count Query
### ============================================
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How many orders do we have?"
}

### Expected:
### - sqlGenerated: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Orders
### - answer: "Found X records"

### ============================================
### Test 6: Top N Query
### ============================================
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me top 10 customers by revenue"
}

### Expected:
### - sqlGenerated: Contains ORDER BY and TOP/LIMIT
### - Multiple steps for schema exploration and SQL generation

