### Test 7: Aggregation Query
### ============================================
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the total revenue by product category?"
}

### Expected:
### - sqlGenerated: Contains GROUP BY and SUM
### - Agent explores schema first

