### ============================================
### Test 15: Get Database Schema
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/schema

### Expected:
### - TablesCount: X
### - Tables array with columns
### - RelationshipsCount: Y

### ============================================
### Test 16: Refresh Schema (Manual Trigger)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/schema/refresh

### Expected:
### - message: "Schema refreshed and re-indexed successfully"
### - tablesCount: X
### - relationshipsCount: Y
### - timestamp: Current time

### ============================================
### Test 17: Conversation Context
### ============================================

# First query
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me customers from New York"
}

###

# Follow-up query (should use context)
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How many are there?"
}

### Expected:
### - Second query understands "there" refers to "customers from New York"
### - Uses conversation context

### ============================================
### Test 18: Error Handling
### ============================================
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "SELECT * FROM NonExistentTable"
}

### Expected:
### - Handles error gracefully
### - May attempt self-correction
### - Returns meaningful error message

