### ============================================
POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show customers who have placed more than 5 orders with total value over $1000"
}

### Expected:
### - Complex SQL with subquery or HAVING clause
### - Multiple reasoning steps
### - Agent breaks down the problem

