### ============================================
### FALLBACK TESTING
### ============================================

### Test 21: Qdrant Fallback Test
### MANUAL: Stop Qdrant first (docker stop qdrant)
### Then run this query

POST {{devEndpoint}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show customers"
}

### Expected:
### - Still succeeds (using keyword fallback)
### - Check logs: "[SchemaRetriever] Using keyword-based retrieval"
### - Response may be slightly different but functional

### MANUAL: Restart Qdrant (docker start qdrant)

### ============================================
### Test 22: Schema Auto-Sync Test
### MANUAL TEST:
### 1. Start API
### 2. Wait 30 seconds
### 3. Check logs: "[SchemaSync] Initial schema hash stored"
### 4. Modify database schema:
###    ALTER TABLE Customers ADD COLUMN TestColumn VARCHAR(100);
### 5. Wait 5 minutes
### 6. Check logs: "[SchemaSync] Schema change detected! Re-indexing..."
### 7. Check logs: "[SchemaSync] ✓ Re-indexing complete"
### 8. Test query to verify new schema is indexed

### ============================================
### Test 23: Retry Logic Test
### MANUAL TEST:
### 1. Temporarily block database connection
### 2. Run query
### 3. Check logs for retry attempts:
###    "[ReActAgent] Tool execution failed, retry 1/3 after 2s"
###    "[ReActAgent] Tool execution failed, retry 2/3 after 4s"
### 4. Unblock database
### 5. Verify query eventually succeeds

### ============================================
### NOTES
### ============================================

# To run all tests:
# 1. Ensure API is running: dotnet run --project TextToSqlAgent.API
# 2. Ensure Qdrant is running: docker start qdrant
# 3. Ensure database is accessible
# 4. Use REST Client extension in VS Code
# 5. Click "Send Request" above each test

# To check logs:
# tail -f TextToSqlAgent.API/logs/api-*.log

# To monitor agent behavior:
# grep "ReActAgent" TextToSqlAgent.API/logs/api-*.log
# grep "SchemaRetriever" TextToSqlAgent.API/logs/api-*.log
# grep "SchemaSync" TextToSqlAgent.API/logs/api-*.log

### ============================================
### SUCCESS CRITERIA
### ============================================

# ✅ All queries return success: true
# ✅ Agent mode shows "ReAct"
# ✅ Multiple steps visible in complex queries
# ✅ Fallback works when Qdrant down
# ✅ Schema auto-sync detects changes
# ✅ Retry logic handles transient failures
# ✅ Vietnamese queries work
# ✅ Out-of-scope queries handled gracefully
# ✅ Schema refresh endpoint works
# ✅ Conversation context maintained
